<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Підтвердження реєстрації</title>
  <style>
    /* Інлайн CSS для стилізації */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #4CAF50;
      text-align: center;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .btn-confirm {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 0.8em;
      color: #666;
      text-align: center;
      opacity: 0.4;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Registration Confirmation</h1>
    <p>Hello, {{name}}!</p>
    <p>Thank you for registering on our platform. To complete the registration process, please confirm your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
    <a href="{{url}}" class="btn-confirm">Confirm Registration</a>
    <p class="footer">If you did not register on our platform, simply ignore this email.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>